- **Also fixed play's random moments playing stuff even when not told to. Lol.**
- **Removed Google command.** Just telling, you might ask.

name: midnight.prefix
desc:
Change your servers prefix by doing %prefix%prefix [prefix] and the bot will respond using that.

The prefix can be anything, it doesn't just have to be a symbol!

actions.message:
Prefix is already set to `${tempVars("tag")}`.
Do a `admin.midnight.prefix <new prefix>` to change it.
